.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, accountant, lawyer, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the paramedic is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the paramedic is on the far right##1
4. the accountant is the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the lawyer is between the fisherman and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Job   | accountant     | lawyer           | fisherman | paramedic  |
| Sport         | cycling | skateboarding | parkour   | rowing |

