.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, whist, monopoly
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the person driving the bus and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | monopoly   | mah-jongg | scrabble | whist      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

