4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Game       | scrabble | poker | chess     | snooker   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

