.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, milk, water
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person drinking juice is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Beverage   | milk          | juice     | water  | coffee     |

