.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, badminton, tennis, water-polo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Sport           | volleyball | water-polo | badminton | tennis     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

