2. the person traveling to berlin is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person traveling to prague is between the person driving the scooter and the person traveling to boston##2
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| City   | hamburg | boston | prague | berlin |
| Transport     | bike     | bus   | subway | scooter  |

