.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, june, july, march
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the polish is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Birthday         | august | june | march     | july    |

